    "subTabDescription": "<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\"><strong>Learn to Ski or Board Package (for complete beginners)</strong></div>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"table text-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\n<th style=\"height: 10px; width: 29.7665%; text-align: center;\"><strong>6 days </strong></th>\n<th style=\"height: 10px; width: 29.1829%; text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong>Child </strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"height: 10px; width: 39.2996%; text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong>Adult </strong></p>\n<p><strong>12 years +</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.7665%; text-align: center;\">Learn to Ski</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.1829%; text-align: center;\">£312 (6-11years)</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 39.2996%; text-align: center;\">£356</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.7665%; text-align: center;\">Learn to Board </td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.1829%; text-align: center;\">\n<p>£337 (8-11years)</p>\n</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 39.2996%; text-align: center;\">£383</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Included for 7 days</p>\n<ul>\n<li>7 day lift pass</li>\n<li>7 day ski bus ticket</li>\n<li>7 days 'Blue' ski/board &amp; boot hire</li>\n<li>5 days tuition (1½ hrs per day)</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Ski or Board Saver Package</strong></p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"table text-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\n<th style=\"height: 10px; width: 29.9611%; text-align: center;\"><strong>6 days</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 31.1284%; text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong>Child </strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"height: 10px; width: 36.965%; text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong>Adult</strong></p>\n<p><strong>12 years +</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.9611%; text-align: center;\">Ski saver</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.1284%; text-align: center;\">£366 (6-11years)</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 36.965%; text-align: center;\">\n<p>£402</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 21px; width: 29.9611%; text-align: center;\">Board saver </td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.1284%; text-align: center;\">£366 (8-11years)</td>\n<td align=\"center\" style=\"height: 21px; width: 36.965%; text-align: center;\">£402</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Included for 7 days </p>\n<ul>\n<li>7 day lift pass</li>\n<li>7 day ski bus ticket</li>\n<li>7 days 'Red' ski/board &amp; boot hire for adults, 'Blue' skis and boots for children</li>\n<li>3 days tuition (1½ per day) ski or snowboard</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Tuition information</strong></p>\n<p>The meeting point for Ski/Snowboard tuition is at <strong>South Point</strong>, about 10-20 mins by ski bus from the centre of Levi. Lessons begin from the excellent beginners area on the south slopes. Ski passes (including ski bus ticket) must be collected from Zero Point in the centre of Levi prior to your lessons. Equipment may be collected/returned to Zero Point or South Point. The ski bus runs every 15 minutes from outside Zero Point and multiple stops around Levi. </p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p>Group tuition needs a minimum number of guests to take place. Very occasionally these numbers aren’t reached. If you have pre-booked tuition and this happens, the ski-school will do their best to offer private tuition to the value of what you had originally booked.</p>\n<p>All Saver Packs must be pre-booked in UK and are not bookable locally.</p>\n<p>Learn To Ski &amp; Board is for<span> </span><span>complete</span><span> </span>beginners only (guests who have never skied). Any guests booking this package who have skied before will be charged an upgrade cost locally.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at time of publishing but may vary up or down. Correct prices will be advised at the time of booking.</strong></p>\n</div>"
  },
