ars</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 45px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 47.0781%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>First Time: 3 Days 1hr30mins</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 21.9977%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 19.8868%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 64px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 47.0781%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>Beginner: 3 Days 1hr30mins</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 21.9977%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 19.8868%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 64px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 47.0781%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>Intermediate: 3 Days 1hr30mins</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 21.9977%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 19.8868%; height: 64px;\">\n<p>£131</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p><strong>Tuition information</strong></p>\n<p>The meeting point for Ski/Snowboard tuition is at South Point, about 10-20 mins by ski bus from the centre of Levi. Lessons begin from the excellent beginners area on the south slopes. Ski passes (including ski bus ticket) must be collected from Zero Point in the centre of Levi prior to your lessons. Equipment may be collected/returned to Zero Point or South Point. The ski bus runs every 15 minutes from outside Zero Point and multiple stops around Levi.</p>\n<p>Group tuition need a minimum number of guests to take place. Very occasionally these numbers aren’t reached. If you have pre-booked tuition and this happens, the ski-school will do their best to offer private tuition to the value of what you had originally booked.</p>\n<p><strong>Ski Bus</strong></p>\n<p>With a valid lift pass you can pay an optional €3 per day to use the resort bus to the ski lifts and around the village. Non-skiers (without a lift pass) can use the ski bus for €4 per day if booked in advance or €4 per trip if purchased on the bus. Children under 6 years travel free with an adult. These optional prices are approximate.</p>\n<p><strong>Levels of tuition</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>First time: never skied before</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Beginner: limited ski experience</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Intermediate: snowplough ski turns, turn on gentle slope</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please ensure you pre-book tuition for high season dates to avoid the ski schools being fully booked.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at time of publishing. Up-to-date prices are confirmed at time of booking.</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
